author: COMSOL
description: A linear guide has been loaded above the manufacturer specification limit. A concern arises whether the contact loads will introduce fatigue spalling. In an analysis of the rolling contact fatigue motion of the mostly loaded rolling element is simulated and fatigue is evaluated using the Dang Van model.
label: linear_guide.mph
